     The radical ${\operatorname{rad}} \left( {C_R ^\lambda  } \right)$ is a right $A$-submodule of $C_R ^\lambda  $  and  ${\operatorname{rad}} \left( {\,_L C^\lambda  } \right)$ is a left $A$-submodule of $\,_L C^\lambda  $.



